pull_request.title: Reworked search for executable files in tests
pull_request.body: I'm sorry, this patch was supposed to be included in my last pull request https://github.com/open-quantum-safe/liboqs/pull/610. Without it, tests do not pass when cross-compiling on Linux. Mingw-w64 builds executables with the ".EXE" extension, which is not expected by the script that runs the tests.
